OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775052666
OL,3,CWegovy announcement a 'major turning
OL,4,Cpoint in the battle against obesity'
OL,6,FThe drug can now be prescribed for
OL,7,Fweight loss or to help reduce the risk
OL,8,Fof major cardiovascular events, as ITV
OL,9,FNews' Phil Sime reports
OL,11,FExperts have described the decision to
OL,12,Fprescribe a weight loss jab for
OL,13,Fpreventing heart attacks and strokes
OL,14,Fas a genuine "win-win", saying the
OL,15,Fmove could be a "major turning point
OL,16,Fin the battle against obesity".
OL,18,FWegovy can now be prescribed for
OL,19,Fweight loss or to help reduce the risk
OL,20,Fof major cardiovascular events.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
