CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775052666
OL,3,CWegovy announcement a 'major turning
OL,4,Cpoint in the battle against obesity'
OL,6,FAcademics said that the decision will
OL,7,Fhelp reduce the risk of disease and
OL,8,Flead to improvements in quality of
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FThey said the treatment has the
OL,12,Fpotential to reduce health
OL,13,Finequalities, as they urged local
OL,14,Fhealth bodies to ensure that there is
OL,15,Fnot a postcode lottery in care when
OL,16,Fthe drugs are rolled out in the summer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
