CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775052666
OL,3,CWegovy announcement a 'major turning
OL,4,Cpoint in the battle against obesity'
OL,6,FBut they also urged prescribers to
OL,7,Fensure the benefit is "balanced
OL,8,Fagainst the risk of side effects",
OL,9,Fhighlighting that GLP-1 receptor
OL,10,Fagonist drugs can reduce muscle mass
OL,11,Fas well as fat.
