CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775052666
OL,3,CWegovy announcement a 'major turning
OL,4,Cpoint in the battle against obesity'
OL,6,FAs a result, people who take them
OL,7,Fshould also engage in physical
OL,8,Factivity such as resistance training,
OL,9,Fwhich may not be feasible in frail
OL,10,Fpatients, experts said.
OL,12,FIt comes as the NHS's spending
OL,13,Fwatchdog, the National Institute for
OL,14,FHealth and Care Excellence (Nice), has
OL,15,Fgiven the green light to giving
OL,16,Fsemaglutide to overweight and obese
OL,17,Fpatients living with certain heart and
OL,18,Fcirculatory conditions to cut their
OL,19,Frisk of a major cardiovascular event.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775052666
OL,3,CWegovy announcement a 'major turning
OL,4,Cpoint in the battle against obesity'
OL,6,FNaveed Sattar, professor of
OL,7,Fcardiometabolic medicine at the
OL,8,FUniversity of Glasgow, said treatments
OL,9,Falso improve patients' quality of life
OL,10,F"in a meaningful way, making this a
OL,11,Fgenuine win`win".
OL,13,F"Given that so many people living with
OL,14,Fcardiovascular disease also struggle
OL,15,Fwith excess weight, it's no longer
OL,16,Fsufficient to focus solely on lipids
OL,17,Fand blood pressure.
OL,19,F"We must also address weight directly
OL,20,Fif we want to deliver the best
OL,21,Fpossible outcomes for our patients."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775052666
OL,3,CWegovy announcement a 'major turning
OL,4,Cpoint in the battle against obesity'
OL,6,FRobert Storey, professor of cardiology
OL,7,Fat the University of Sheffield, said:
OL,8,F"Prescribing of semaglutide needs to
OL,9,Fbe appropriately targeted since GLP-1
OL,10,Fdrugs can reduce muscle mass as well
OL,11,Fas fat so physical activity, such as
OL,12,Fresistance training, is important to
OL,13,Fcounteract potential negative effects
OL,14,Fon muscle strength, which may not be
OL,15,Ffeasible in frail people.
OL,17,F"The benefits also need to be balanced
OL,18,Fagainst the risk of side effects.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
