OL,3,CWegovy announcement a 'major turning
OL,4,Cpoint in the battle against obesity'
OL,6,F"These issues and the need for
OL,7,Ftraining people to inject the drug as
OL,8,Fwell as ongoing monitoring and
OL,9,Fprescribing requires the allocation of
OL,10,FNHS resources to ensure the benefits
OL,11,Fof this Nice guidance can be fully
OL,12,Frealised."
